<div class="home-rolling mt-4">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6" >
                <div class="rolling-content" >
                    <h3>About Us</h3>
                    <p style="font-weight: 800;">Cocycle was set up in August 2020 under its original name Two Wheels Better, with the intention of creating a bike buddy system that people could use to commute together on two wheels. The idea was initially very well received with 70-80 people signing up (possibly motivated by free samosas at our launch event), and the first rides started happening shortly afterwards. We were able to show various people their routes to work by bike, and even took a plucky sixth former to college. It also became clear that a lot of people wanted to have a service that would help them with very basic cycling skills prior to any attempt to commute by bike. Many of our experienced members travelled far and wide across the city to meet this need, taking people for rides along towpaths or in their local parks to help them build the confidence they needed to get in the saddle for themselves.</p>
                    @*<div class="btn-wrapper desktop-left mt-5 mt-md-0 padding-bottom-10">
