    </div>
</div>

<div class="home-rolling mt-4">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class="rolling-content">

                    <p style="font-weight: 800;">
                        Unfortunately the 2nd and 3rd waves of the coronavirus pandemic put pay to our activities for many months as encouraging people to meet up for bike rides contravened social distancing guidelines. During this time we hunkered down and decided to create a website / web app to automate the process of connecting existing cyclists with people who want to find their wheels. We re-invented ourselves as cocycle and continued to arrange further commutes and social rides between people who signed up to our services once it became permissible again. With the website complete we are now offering a peer to peer service that people anywhere can use to offer or seek help cycling, and we hope you enjoy it!
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


